content: How do I view a list of events I previously signed up for?
Hi Mary! You can sign in to https://events.democrats.org and go to the drop-down menu on the top right-hand side and select "my schedule"

Please let me know if this works for you or if you need further assistance! Thanks so much for signing up to heed the call and "Do Something!" üí™üèº <:michelle:1275836570544635992> <a:kamala3:1269028076663345152>
